data.description:
Discover this inviting bi-level home in the heart of Loveland, offering a spacious layout with wood floors, a delightful covered patio for outdoor relaxation, and a large backyard that's perfect for gardening enthusiasts. The kitchen boasts new stainless steel appliances for added modernization, and it's conveniently close to the elementary school! 
Don't miss this rare opportunity to make this your new home!
